141.795, 141.2797, 140.2277, 140.2509, 140.5968, 140.9198, 140.8945, 141.7978, 140.8903, 140.1642, 138.9669, 139.688, 139.8683, 139.6611, 140.0555, 139.7113, 140.0586, 140.9795, 140.3721, 140.5957, 140.1335, 139.8971, 139.9059, 138.4442, 137.8356, 137.6022, 137.5953, 137.3728, 136.7656, 136.3308, 136.2186, 136.2598, 135.7818, 135.7483, 135.6991, 136.0626, 135.8023, 136.2976, 137.1836, 136.4506, 135.7998, 135.4722, 135.7101, 136.1279, 135.9317, 135.3237, 135.0704, 134.1061, 133.4719, 133.9624, 133.3863, 133.8707, 134.625, 136.1603, 135.9732, 136.2722, 138.7058, 137.1372, 135.49, 137.7867, 136.311, 138.6385, 139.3435, 139.3301, 140.4175, 139.7768, 139.9336, 140.5499, 140.7816, 139.9198, 140.4801, 139.7747, 139.9423, 140.3475, 141.1275, 140.1948, 140.7873, 141.1016, 141.2578, 139.8659, 141.3941, 141.2786, 140.7082, 139.4134, 139.4289, 140.1039, 139.6441, 139.8834, 140.2584, 140.6054, 140.8454, 140.7325, 140.5891, 140.3417, 140.5067, 140.733, 141.1451, 141.7847, 141.6194, 142.0692, 142.3769, 142.0384, 143.224, 142.7849, 143.4914, 142.9003, 143.3339, 143.5985, 142.5413, 142.8211, 142.5335, 142.6661, 142.3866, 141.6907, 141.3703, 141.8504, 141.8, 141.9775, 141.8757, 143.9897, 144.393, 144.8374, 144.5993, 144.9827, 145.7282, 145.9094, 147.5443, 148.3958, 149.8062, 150.5473, 150.3975, 151.0014, 149.307, 149.0558, 150.0658, 149.68, 148.539, 148.3948, 147.7836, 147.5541], "summary_html": "<h1>20241205_calendar_标准化的未预期盈余</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>将股票 SUE（标准化未预期盈余）忠实迁移到商品期货，严格对齐研报口径：以日频数据中的 <code>profit</code>（每手合约日频加工利润 / 现货隐含利润，替代 EPS）为盈利代理。<strong>季节性（同比）盈余预差</strong> sue_surprise = profit − profit.shift(252)（当前对上一年同期，对应研报「第 t 季度 EPS − 第 t−4 季度 EPS」）；再除以该预差的 <strong>4 个季度（≈252 日）滚动标准差</strong>（std4q，min_periods=126）得到标准化的 SUE_yoy_std4q。对该 SUE 做每日截面百分位排名，映射为 [-1, 1] 连续仓位（scale=2.0），每 20 个交易日 rebalance 一次（h20）。仓位再经 postprocess 的 <code>_ts</code> 时序标准化（每品种 5 年滚动 z-score，min 1 年）处理（变体后缀 <code>_ts</code>）。盈利同比意外向上的品种做多、向下的做空，属 PEAD（盈余公告后漂移）类基本面因子。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<p>数值来自 repro eval（变体 <code>SUEyoy_std4q_h20_ts</code>）；prod OOS 全期回测由 /prod oos 步骤重算。</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (含费, repro eval)</td><td><strong>0.8846</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (无费)</td><td><strong>0.8965</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>231.7%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>258.5%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-63.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>2.221</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>2283</td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.63 / 1.27</td></tr></table></div>\n<p>注：<code>_ts</code> 时序 z-score + gross 归一化使收益/波动量级偏大，Sharpe 为核心口径。</p>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.00</td><td>0.94</td><td>0.77</td><td>0.47</td><td>0.46</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.10</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.73</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.01</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.83</span></td><td>1.77</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>profit</code></td><td>利润</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 20 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 20 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>2284</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>75.9% (多 38.6% / 空 37.3%)</td></tr><tr><td>空仓占比</td><td>24.1%</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>YR</code></td><td><code>252</code></td><td>同比（YoY）季节性 lag，≈1 年交易日</td></tr><tr><td><code>Q</code></td><td><code>63</code></td><td>≈1 季度交易日</td></tr><tr><td><code>STD_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>4 * Q = 252</code></td><td>std4q：SUE 标准化的滚动窗口（4 季度）</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>h20 rebalance/hold</td></tr><tr><td><code>BEST_VARIANT</code></td><td><code>&quot;SUEyoy_std4q_h20&quot;</code></td><td>postprocess 处理 <code>_ts</code> 后缀（时序标准化）</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.96s</li>\n</ul>"}